title: Jonsborg
typeOfFood: Vegan-friendly, Lacto, American, Western, Fast food, Take-out, Non-veg
description: Serves meat, veg options available. Fast food stand selling foods like burgers, sausages, and hot dogs. Has a vegan menu that includes vegan bratwurst, vegan spicy chorizo, vegan burgers, vegan chicken for tacos, and Tzay. Vegan sauces offered. The owner is knowledgeable about ingredients and sources of the vegan products. Happy hour with 2 for 1 specials 18:00-20:00.
